Scholarship.Name: Charles Todd Caldwell Memorial Scholarship
Scholarship.Description:
Preference shall be given to a junior or senior.  This scholarship may follow the student throughout their remaining semestewrs at ENC as long as they meet the following criterion.
/n
/nA: The student shall be majoring in history. In light of this, the chairman of the History Department shall be consulted in regard to potential recipients
/n
/nB: The student must demonstrate financial need.
